{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/Why-being-gratitude-is-needed","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"0deccbde-b4b2-5460-8f59-f325770cbeb1","html":"<p><img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/35059428/85985208-fc1f9400-ba1c-11ea-9c92-7ba8ece59333.jpg\" alt=\"Being gratitude\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"being-gratitude-why-it-needs\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#being-gratitude-why-it-needs\" aria-label=\"being gratitude why it needs permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Being Gratitude why it needs?</h2>\n<p>Even some rich people said, ‘Being Gratitude’ is the key to gain more yield Whatever I do.\nIn my thought, When we say someone ‘Thanks’ with honest heart, the receiver release ‘Oxytocin’ which is feeling of happiness.</p>\n<p>Then we feel so happy and find out our next step.</p>\n<h2 id=\"it-gives-the-pleasure-for-receiver-and-presenter-both\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#it-gives-the-pleasure-for-receiver-and-presenter-both\" aria-label=\"it gives the pleasure for receiver and presenter both permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>It gives the pleasure for receiver and presenter both.</h2>\n<p>‘Oh giving something to him or helping him is giving me the pleasure as well’</p>\n<h2 id=\"it-can-prevent-an-argument-gets-growing-up\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#it-can-prevent-an-argument-gets-growing-up\" aria-label=\"it can prevent an argument gets growing up permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>It can prevent an argument gets growing up.</h2>\n<p>It can even prevent a criticism to be shut down.\nWhen someone just want to advice about my result, then just you can reply ‘Thank you for your feed back’. Then no more criticism would be growing up from his mouth.</p>\n<h3 id=\"even-you-can-gives-a-good-impression-to-people\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#even-you-can-gives-a-good-impression-to-people\" aria-label=\"even you can gives a good impression to people permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><a href=\"https://jamesclear.com/say-thank-you\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Even you can gives a good impression to people</a></h3>\n<p>Besides, I can give him a good impression or 3rd one who saw that my stance. They would gain more opportunity to like me or at least, we can lesser our distributions through this way. There are a tons of people who want to handle us like this. ‘GGon-Dae’.\nJust we need to say ‘Thank you for feed back, that I have a lot to learn’</p>\n<p>And there is a lot additional profit\nDopamine and Serotonin keeps coming out</p>\n<h3 id=\"dopamine-just-empowers-your-activities\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#dopamine-just-empowers-your-activities\" aria-label=\"dopamine just empowers your activities permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Dopamine just empowers your activities.</h3>\n<p>Dopamine is the neurotransmitter to put myself into vicious circle. The circle will keep myself in happiness.\nDopamine also engages with motivation. When you feel dopamine, thus you feel happy from that action, then you do more of it.</p>\n<h2 id=\"appreciating-myself-also-benefits-myself\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#appreciating-myself-also-benefits-myself\" aria-label=\"appreciating myself also benefits myself permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Appreciating myself also benefits myself.</h2>\n<p>Gratitude, no matter what it is targeting to, It releases Dopamine and Serotonin, which is happy hormone.\nEven when we say it from in front of a mirror. We can gain more profit from gratitude effect.</p>\n<h2 id=\"writing-gratitude-journal-for-your-living\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#writing-gratitude-journal-for-your-living\" aria-label=\"writing gratitude journal for your living permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Writing gratitude journal for your living.</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://positivepsychology.com/neuroscience-of-gratitude/#:~:text=When%20we%20express%20gratitude%20and,feel%20happy%20from%20the%20inside.\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Consciously practicing gratitude strengthen our neural pathways.</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<figure> <img src=\"https://positivepsychology.com/wp-content/uploads/gratitude-social-benefits.jpg\" alt=\"the virtous circle of gratitude\">\n<figcaption>Image from https://positivepsychology.com<figcaption>\n</figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n<h3 id=\"then-what-we-have-to-do\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#then-what-we-have-to-do\" aria-label=\"then what we have to do permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Then what we have to do?</h3>\n<p>As we can see, the happy hormones comes out when we say ‘Thanks’. Then It does just increase the feeling of well-being.</p>\n<p>Besides, when a community fulfilled with the members who say easily praise others and themselves, are gain more gratitude effects themselves.</p>\n<p>The dopamine and serotonin. The hormones strengthen the community’s well-being and interpersonal vibe. Thus obviously link to greater productivity.</p>\n<p>Our society isn’t quite happy in the feeling of each individuals. We can see that is symptom of lack of gratitude for each other.\nWhen we say Thanks to other’s judgement, we can cut the chain of vicious circle of unhappiness.\nHope more awareness on the effect of happiness.</p>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/Why-being-gratitude-is-needed","tagSlugs":["/tag/neuroscience/","/tag/habit/","/tag/interpersonal-skill/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2020-06-29T23:46:37.121Z","description":"Wrote the reason why we need to learn about being gratitude. It creates a virtuous circle near of us. Besides, It improves each individuals well-being and immunity as Dopamine, Serotonin, Oxytocin comes out","tags":["neuroscience","habit","interpersonal skill"],"title":"Why being gratitude is needed?","socialImage":"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/35059428/85985208-fc1f9400-ba1c-11ea-9c92-7ba8ece59333.jpg"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/Why-being-gratitude-is-needed